BUSINESS CLOSINGS; ADELANTO (CA) -- PUBLIC FACILITIES; ORANGE COUNTY -- 
GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; ORANGE COUNTY -- TRANSPORTATION; FLYING 
</P>
