Commerce and Industry, left, discusses U.S. business opportunities with Susan 
Lentz, executive director of the World Trade Center Assn. of Orange County, and 
Wahib BinzagrCQ, who is chairman of the Saudi Cairo Bank. LACY ATKINS / Los 
Angeles Times; Map, SAUDI ARABIA , Los Angeles Times 
</P>
