teammates after getting his sixth no-hitter. Associated Press; Photo, (A2) One 
for the Books: There has never been a pitcher like Nolan Ryan, shown here being 
congratulated by Texas catcher John Russell after the 43-year-old had pitched 
his record sixth no-hitter. 
</P>
